<item>
            <title>[DERBY-6973] Provide SHA-512 checksums on future releases</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6973</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Releases have md5 sum for signatures, and nothing modern.  How is this even possible?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
